{"tid":1723485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［管理］如何令一個群體有效運作","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:26:53.000Z","uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d152a275fb79fb40774f7f1aa910e607ed240a12","tid":1723485,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"1. 不捉鬼 - 捉鬼=自我消秏。一個群體時間 精力 士氣有限，花費精力 時間互相懷疑 猜忌 消秏士氣，不如討論如何落實行動 目標 日程 比大圍一個預期計劃<br />\n<br />\n2. 不公審 - 公開指責只對敵人使用。係連登講，不如自己坐低講。公開指責必然導致分邊，分裂，要共容請私下溝通。<br />\n<br />\n3. 不安份 - 無所事事 必然會令人心浮動，沒事找事做不是浪費而是訓練，少少的目標，容易達成的工作，比大圍增加成功感，增加士氣，增加團結度。"},{"pid":"9cca8344baefebc70b816e62b92d083cf206e6ff","tid":1723485,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f36b97d4f6374c1bd469e05c671108d0387712","tid":1723485,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2908c662d2c7910ec9a37d7bee76c3931b37d4","tid":1723485,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"25b391de73677ee27c1c18cbf3d18dd9c7ae233f","tid":1723485,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}